title: Pat Martino Interview 2 with Diane Dayton at Berks Jazz Fest
description: Pat Martino talks to Diane Dayton at the 18th annual VF Outlet Berks Jazz Fest.  In this second interview Pat talks about the here and now, living in the moment. Pat shares his thoughts on redefining life and jazz., and what he is experiencing when playing to an audience.
fulltitle: Pat Martino Interview 2 with Diane Dayton at Berks Jazz Fest
